                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "削月築陽真君曾為申鶴卜卦。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "「卦象顯示，申鶴的命格既犯孤辰，又沖劫煞，殺性極重，是千年難遇、傷人傷己的大凶命格。」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3335,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/18/7998136/5bc9df1fb67391e4c8080da3d855de53_5998673652795638003.png",
                      "name": "瑤瑤",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "瑤瑤見過許多仙人，削月築陽真君就是其中之一。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
